00:47:22.360 --> 00:47:23.020
<v Nate>It's sort of there.</v>

00:47:23.080 --> 00:47:29.340
<v Nate>I mean, I find like the unconscious as a conceptual thing throughout this.</v>

00:47:29.400 --> 00:47:32.420
<v Nate>I mean, withdrawal – or maybe non-conscious, right?</v>

00:47:32.420 --> 00:47:43.460
<v Nate>I mean, performativity is all about sort of non-conscious habitualizations of, you know, social or political or economic imperatives, right?</v>

00:47:43.520 --> 00:47:45.440
