00:47:45.580 --> 00:47:47.540
<v Nate>I mean, clearly he doesn't have the word for it.</v>

00:47:47.840 --> 00:47:51.020
<v Nate>But to me, it's like performativity is almost the bad thing, right?</v>

00:47:51.500 --> 00:47:56.480
