00:47:56.480 --> 00:47:58.060
<v John>OK, so that's the thing.</v>

00:47:58.280 --> 00:48:03.840
<v John>But it's like it's – for me, what I mean when I say performativity is that the enactment precedes the subject, right?</v>

00:48:03.920 --> 00:48:07.160
<v John>Like there is – the action comes first.</v>

00:48:07.380 --> 00:48:17.320
<v John>And he's interested in – and to that extent, it can't possibly be utilitarian calculus because there would be nothing to utilitarianize, right?</v>

00:48:17.480 --> 00:48:19.600
