00:51:13.920 --> 00:51:21.380
<v John>I mean he is – that to me is the generous read, which Nathaniel has been offering so far, which Nathaniel – that's become the role that you've assumed.</v>

00:51:21.520 --> 00:51:26.040
<v John>You're like I'm going to do the affirmative reading for everything, which is great.</v>

00:51:26.240 --> 00:51:26.920
