00:55:18.200 --> 00:55:33.840
<v John>Like I – even though I know in the back of my head that we're going to get to a place where, oh, that craftsman who builds the cabinet isn't sort of superior or true or allowing the – I mean, when he uses the phrase like what the form of the wood wants, I just go like, oh, my fucking God.</v>

00:55:33.900 --> 00:55:42.840
<v Nathaniel>Like the terms matter, the forms slumbering within it, which would be like a multiple – like it wouldn't be a form.</v>

00:55:43.020 --> 00:55:51.400
