00:57:52.740 --> 00:58:09.280
<v John>But again, I mean partly I feel like what I come up against with Heidegger is I'm frequently faced with having to do a lot of work on particular locutions in order to make them not resonate with me the way that they just instinctively do repeatedly.</v>

00:58:09.820 --> 00:58:17.720
<v Nate>You know, it's also like affirmation – affirmative readings don't have to preclude confrontations with the text either.</v>

00:58:18.000 --> 00:58:18.620
